			 When Sarah wakes up, what time is it in Hong Kong?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q1" >Pic A</a></li><li><a id="q2" >Pic B</a></li><li><a id="q3" >Pic C</a></li><li><a id="q4" >Pic D</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="2">What time is the plane due to arrive at Heathrow?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q5" >Pic A</a></li><li><a id="q6" >Pic B</a></li><li><a id="q7" >Pic C</a></li><li><a id="q8" >Pic D</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="3">What does Peter decide to order for breakfast?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q9" >Pic A</a></li><li><a id="q10" >Pic B</a></li><li><a id="q11" >Pic C</a></li><li><a id="q12" >Pic D</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="4">What does Sarah plan to have for breakfast?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q13" >Pic A</a></li><li><a id="q14" >Pic B</a></li><li><a id="q15" >Pic C</a></li><li><a id="q16" >Pic D</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="5">What does Peter's suitcase look like?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q17" >Pic A</a></li><li><a id="q18" >Pic B</a></li><li><a id="q19" >Pic C</a></li><li><a id="q20" >Pic D</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="6">What does Sarah's brother look like?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q21" >Pic A</a></li><li><a id="q22" >Pic B</a></li><li><a id="q23" >Pic C</a></li><li><a id="q24" >Pic D</a></li></ol><br/></li></ol>
